  "headline": "Founder & CEO at SJK Group | The leading out-of-home media agency in Vietnam",
  "summary": "Hi my friends, <br><br>At the helm of SJK Group, I have been driven by a passion for building a leading OOH company in Vietnam through innovation, customer-centric philosophy and operational excellence. I firmly believe that OOH Industry has evolved beyond a traditional business driven by technology, and data-driven insights and innovative solutions that benefit both customers and brands.<br><br>I have held various positions in local & international OOH associations: Managing member of Vietnam Advertising Association (VAA), chairman of Vietnam's biggest OOH community club (OOHClub), Vice chairman of Hochiminh Advertising Association (HAA) and Vietnam’s only representative member of WOOH (World Out-out-home organization). These roles provided me with invaluable insights into both the global & local markets and strengthen SJK Group’s relationships with Vietnam’s Advertising policy regulators, strategic partners & most important, our valued clients who trust our services and team.<br><br>SJK Group is a group of unit businesses that align with SJK’s goals and long-term strategy:<br>- Compass Technology JSC - Vietnam OOH industry insider &  OOH performance tracking <br>- Wi5 JSC - Top 3 Wifi marketing company in Vietnam<br>- Look at Media - Outdoor LED & LED Panel media owner company",
